                        "displayName": "wangbo",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "    protected function _initDb()\r\n    {\r\n        \/\/...\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    protected function _initAutoloader()\r\n    {\r\n        $autoloader = new Zend_Application_Module_Autoloader(array(\r\n            'namespace' => '',\r\n            'basePath' => APPLICATION_PATH,\r\n        ));\r\n\r\n        return $autoloader;\r\n    }",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=wangbo",
                        "name": "wangbo",
                        "displayName": "wangbo",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-10-23T01:25:32.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-10-23T01:25:32.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/35493",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Why are you initializing a unique database connection in each module? I'd do this in your application bootstrap, and then do only module-specific initialization in your module bootstraps.\r\n\r\nSecond: your individual module bootstraps should extend Zend_Application_Module_Bootstrap, which will negate the need for your _initAutoloader() method (as this support is built-in).",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-10-23T11:57:14.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-10-23T11:57:14.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/35494",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I'm closing this as \"not an issue\"; the bootstrapping for the reporter's application should be modified to make better usage of resources and the design of the ZF bootstrap mechanisms.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
